rows.label: qst502017_msg0001
rows.name:
You look tired, Chancellor. Shall
I give you a shoulder massage?

rows.label: qst502017_msg0002
rows.name:
Oh, thank you... In that case,
I'll take you up on your offer...

rows.label: qst502017_msg0004
rows.name: Oh... That was a wonderful massage.

rows.label: qst502017_msg0005
rows.name:
The pleasant lightning stimulation
has lightened my shoulders. It's
like a weight has been lifted...

rows.label: qst502017_msg0006
rows.name:
When my granddaughter gives me a
massage, I feel a year younger...

rows.label: qst502017_msg0007
rows.name:
But when Raiko-dono does it,
I feel twenty years younger.

rows.label: qst502017_msg0008
rows.name:
I'm so happy to receive such
praise. Shall I do it again?

rows.label: qst502017_msg0009
rows.name:
You must be busy, Raiko-dono. As much
as I'd like to, I shall refrain.

rows.label: qst502017_msg0010
rows.name:
Besides, if I become forty years
younger, I'll be even more
mischievous than His Highness.

rows.label: qst502017_msg0013
rows.name:
No, I'm quite alright! I have a
terribly bad feeling about this!
